scene.message:
Nanjo: I see. So you've{nl}
met the masked man{nl}
as well, Sonomura.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Meeting a creepy old{nl}
geezer like that is{nl}
nothing to be glad about!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: That dream with the{nl}
butterfly man-{nl}
Ayase's had it too.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Nobody's here...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
You think that Kurouri guy{nl}
played us for fools?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: But the Kurouri of{nl}
this world seemed{nl}
trustworthy enough...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Hm? What's that?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh, it's that butterfly-{nl}
the one from when{nl}
Maki's mother collapsed.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Pretty butterfly, huh?{nl}
Should we catch it{nl}
and keep it as a pet?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Nanjo, you into{nl}
butterflies or somethin'?{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't tell me you're the{nl}
type with a room full of{nl}
pinned bugs, grinning at 'em?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: {wait_fr:32}...Don't tell me{nl}
it's his trap?{wait_fr:21}{nl}
One funny move and I'll{nl}
catch it and crush it.{waitkey}{ret}
